name: Wiener Blut
wikiSummary: Wiener Blut is the 7th song from the album 'Liebe ist für alle da'. The song is thought to be about the Fritzl case.  When played live, baby dolls drop from the ceiling and green lasers shoot from their eyes. Later on in the song, these individually explode.
wikiText:
Wiener Blut is the 7th song from the album 'Liebe ist für alle da'. The song is thought to be about the Fritzl case.
 
 When played live, baby dolls drop from the ceiling and green lasers shoot from their eyes. Later on in the song, these individually explode.
